nodes.text: Kharulu Neen was an individual who died as a result of the New Republic's actions by the time of the Battle of Jakku in 5 ABY. In the midst of the battle, Palal Seedia, a TIE fighter pilot of the Galactic Empire's 204th Imperial Fighter Wing, lamented Neen and other comrades she had lost to the New Republic during a confrontation with the New Republic pilot Wyl Lark.
Kharulu Neen was mentioned in the 2021 novel Victory's Price, written by Alexander Freed.
